{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_52_03",
  "title": "miho 3話 虫ケラ以下の脳味噌が！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……それでですね、星見プロのみんなを\nもっと大勢の人に知ってもらいたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ you see‚ I want more people\nto get to know everyone at Hoshimi Pro‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "最近ずっと企画書を練っていてこの間も夜中の三時\nでした。その疲れが抜けなくて……俺ももう歳ですかね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I’ve been working on proposals nonstop—just the other night it was 3 a.m.\nI still haven’t shaken off the fatigue… Am I getting old already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 16.6467561085
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……その台詞、私が貴方より年上だというのを\n承知の上で吐いたなら、勇気だけは褒めて差し上げます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If you said that knowing full well\nthat I’m older than you‚ I’ll at least commend your courage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 24.7430146853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、マネージャーが激務なのは知っていますけどね\nはぁ……仕事熱心なのは大変結構だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I do know that being a manager is demanding.\nSigh… Being devoted to your work is all well and good‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "なんで私が貴方の夢を聞かされているのかしら\nそういう話は他の子にいくらでも出来るでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but why am I the one listening to your dreams?\nYou have plenty of other girls you could talk to about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 41.3049673399
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……あら、この鹿肉、美味しいわね\nはぁ……料理が美味しいのが唯一の救いだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh my‚ this venison is delicious.\nSigh… The good food is the only saving grace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7333318075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 52.7030537607
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、鹿肉のローストとこちらの赤ワインを……\nええ、ボトルでお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ the roasted venison and this red wine‚ please…\nYes‚ a full bottle‚ please.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3999984742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "い、一番高いのじゃないですか、しかもボトルで……\nその、昼間もワイナリーで試飲したんですよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that’s the most expensive one—even a whole bottle…\nYou tasted wine at the winery earlier today too‚ right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0784164748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 68.6553209943
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "奢ると言ったのは貴方ですからね\nこれは貴方の話を聞いてあげている、正当な報酬です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re the one who said it’s on you.\nThis is fair compensation for listening to you talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.3666651409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "貴方こそ、わざわざ居酒屋に入ったなら\nもう少し食べるか飲むかしたらどうなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As for you‚ since you went out of your way to come to an izakaya‚\nwhy don’t you eat or drink a bit more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.0333318075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.6623050374
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺は夕方、愛に付き合ってラーメンを食べたので……\n夜は控えめにしておかないと、その……太りそうですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had ramen earlier this evening with Ai‚ so…\nif I’m not careful at night‚ I might‚ um… gain weight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3666651409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんも、明日も旅程があることですし\nお酒はほどほどにしてですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And you have another day of travel tomorrow‚ miho-san‚\nso maybe we should keep the drinking moderate…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0387431703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "…………この、虫ケラ以下の脳味噌が！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You brainless insect!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.9112620992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 96.9112620992
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 101.1526680949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "居酒屋で酒を飲まないなどと……\nその矛盾にすら、貴様では気付くことも出来んのか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not drinking alcohol at an izakaya…\nAre you too stupid to notice that contradiction!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.7666651409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "挙げ句、人にたらたらと長話をしおって！\n私は慰安旅行なぞ断固辞退すると言ったのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And on top of that‚ you drone on endlessly!\nI told you outright I was refusing this so-called recreational trip!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9333318075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.9093348189
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、旅行中はfranとkanaの\n面倒を見ずに済むのだけは幸いと思ったら！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ I thought at least\nI wouldn’t have to babysit fran and kana during the trip!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4333318075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 125.8567949617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "道中、遙子どころか琴乃にまで質問攻めにされて！\n「バラエティでどう振る舞ったらいいですか」だなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yet on the way‚ not just Haruko but even Kotono bombarded me with questions!\n“How should I act on variety shows‚” they ask!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4333318075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.6122597382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "笑いを取りたいと言うなら\n他に聞くべき相手がいくらでもいるだろう！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If they want to get laughs‚\nthere are plenty of other people they should be asking!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.9333318075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはお手数をおかけしました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m sorry for the trouble…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1650261884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "――それから、貴様！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—And another thing‚ you!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4177246417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 142.4177246417
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 145.3925772355
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "食べ過ぎると太るだのと、小賢しいことを！\n貴様ごとき下っ端は、食うのも仕事のうちだろうが！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saying you’ll gain weight if you eat too much—what a petty excuse!\nFor a lowly underling like you‚ eating is part of the job!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3999984742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも貴様、いつもろくなものを食べてないだろう！\nあんな餌で労働のエネルギーを賄える訳あるか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t even eat proper meals most of the time!\nHow do you expect to fuel your work with food like that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.6666651409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 164.4277475363
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "食って寝て、馬車馬のように働く！\nそれがウジ虫の貴様が人間になる、唯一の道である！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eat‚ sleep‚ and work like a beast of burden!\nThat’s the only way a maggot like you can become human!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.4333318075,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knife-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8038.919130400018,
          "startTime": 172.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 173.9525089587
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、フォークをこっちに向けないで下さい！！\n食べます、自分で食べられますから！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "P-Please don’t point the fork at me!!\nI’ll eat! I can feed myself!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.7333318075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
