      "text": "鹿肉と、こっちの唐揚げも美味いぞ！\nああ、しかし肉ばかりでも栄養が偏ってしまうな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The venison and this fried chicken are good too!\nAh‚ but eating only meat will throw off the nutritional balance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.6536448247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
