      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "も、もうさっきのボトルが空に……！\nmihoさん、まだお酒注文するんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-the last bottle is already empty…!\nmiho-san‚ you’re ordering more alcohol!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.1666651409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
