      "text": "当たり前だ！　貴様がこれを完食するまで\n私が見張っていてやらなければいけないからな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! Until you finish all of this‚\nI have to keep watch over you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.3999984742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
