      "text": "（酔っ払ってキツい口調になってるけど）\n（前々から、俺の食生活を心配されてたんだろうか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s drunk and her tone is harsh‚）\n（but maybe she’s been worried about my diet for a long time…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.7333318075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
